---
title: "VineMind AI — Recommendation State Machine"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Generated : Water Stress Model<br/>produces score

    Generated --> Pending : Decision Intelligence<br/>Engine assigns<br/>recommendation

    state Pending {
        [*] --> AwaitingReview
        AwaitingReview : Recommendation displayed<br/>on dashboard
    }

    Pending --> Accepted : User approves<br/>irrigation action

    Pending --> Dismissed : User dismisses<br/>with reason

    Pending --> Expired : valid_until<br/>timestamp passed

    Accepted --> Completed : Irrigation<br/>confirmed executed

    Accepted --> Reverted : User reverses<br/>decision

    Completed --> [*]
    Reverted --> [*]

    state Dismissed {
        [*] --> ReasonCaptured
        ReasonCaptured : User provides<br/>dismissal reason
        ReasonCaptured --> Logged
        Logged : Logged to<br/>audit trail
    }

    Dismissed --> [*]

    Expired --> [*]

    note right of Generated
        Stress Score: 0-100
        Category assigned
        Confidence calculated
        DEP created
    end note

    note right of Pending
        Priority ranked
        Action assigned:
        - Irrigate Immediately (81-100)
        - Irrigate Tonight (61-80)
        - Delay/Monitor (21-60)
        - No Action (0-20)
    end note

    note right of Accepted
        Timestamp logged
        User identity recorded
        Audit trail created
    end note

    note right of Dismissed
        Reason required
        Cannot be re-accepted
        Historical record preserved
    end note
